  <div class="email-body">
    <h1>Your offer was accepted!</h1>
    <p>Hi {{buyer_name}},</p>
    <p>
      Congratulations — the seller has selected your offer. The deal is now moving
      forward to the contract stage.
    </p>

    <div class="info-box">
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Property</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{address}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Accepted Offer</span>
        <span class="info-value">${{formatNumber bid_price}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Seller</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{seller_name}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>
      A purchase contract will be generated shortly. You'll receive another
      notification when it's ready for your signature.
    </p>

    <div class="btn-wrap">
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/listings/{{listing_id}}" class="btn">View Property Details</a>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" />
    <p class="muted">
      Please ensure your proof of funds and any required documents are up to date
      in your account before the contract is issued.
    </p>
  </div>
